quran[17{c,v,t}:
103,1,Wal' asr
103,2,Innal insaana lafee khusr
103,3,Il lal lazeena aamanu wa 'amilus saali haati wa tawa saw bil haqqi wa tawa saw bis sabr
104,1,Wai lul-li kulli hu mazatil-lumaza
104,2,Al-lazi jama'a maalaw wa'addadah
104,3,Yahsabu anna maalahu akhladah
104,4,Kalla layum ba zanna fil hutamah
104,5,Wa maa adraaka mal-hutamah
104,6,Narul laahil-mooqada
104,7,Al latee tat tali'u 'alalafidah
104,8,Innaha 'alaihim moosada
104,9,Fee 'amadim-mu mad dadah
105,1,Alam tara kaifa fa'ala rabbuka bi ashaabil feel
105,2,Alam yaj'al kai dahum fee tad leel
105,3,Wa arsala 'alaihim tairan abaabeel
105,4,Tar meehim bi hi jaaratim min sij jeel
105,5,Faja 'alahum ka'asfim m'akool
